<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activation Code</title>
    <style>
      /* Reset styles for email clients */
      body,
      table,
      td,
      th {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        border: 0;
      }
      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 100%;
      }
      td,
      th {
        padding: 12px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      /* Email container */
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      /* Header style */
      .header {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      /* Content style */
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      /* Activation code style */
      .activation-code {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Activation Code</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= user.name %></p>
        <p>
          Thank you for signing up with our service. To activate your account,
          please use the following activation code:
        </p>
        <p class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
          contact our support team.
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Your Company Learning Hub</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
